To build just the firmware:

   catkin_make arduino_firmware_jet_binary

To flash to an Arduino UNO (on /dev/ttyACM0):

   catkin_make arduino_firmware_jet_binary-upload

To run the node:

   rosrun rosserial_python serial_node.py /dev/ttyACM0

   or with roslaunch:

      roslaunch arduino arduino.launch
